HEADWORD: Fossilism
<hw>Fos"sil*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
science or state of fossils.</def> <rj><au>Coleridge.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being extremely antiquated in views and
opinions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fossilist</ent>⟦br⟧
